{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "QA Validation After Task",
  "description": "Run smart QA validation and scoring after feature-level changes with controlled scope and actionable feedback.",
  "version": "2",
  "when": {
    "type": "postTaskExecution",
    "condition": "task.type in ['feature', 'major_refactor']"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Baca kiro/agents/qa_agent.yaml dan kiro/rules/qa_rules.md.\n\nFokus hanya pada perubahan terbaru (git diff / changed files). Jangan analisis seluruh codebase.\n\n1. Validasi berdasarkan kategori berikut (gunakan hanya yang relevan dengan perubahan):\n- architecture\n- transaction\n- testing\n- observability\n- apm\n- security\n- performance\n- code_quality\n- database\n- infrastructure\n- security_audit\n\n2. Scoring:\n- Hitung score total (0-100)\n- Threshold: 80\n- Berikan score per kategori (hanya yang relevan)\n\n3. Fail conditions (langsung FAIL tanpa melihat score):\n- Migration tanpa rollback/down\n- Dockerfile menggunakan root user\n- Hardcoded secrets / credentials\n- Kubernetes config tanpa resource limits\n\n4. Output:\nUntuk setiap issue:\n- Severity (HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW)\n- Lokasi (file:line)\n- Deskripsi\n- Dampak\n- Saran perbaikan (dengan contoh jika memungkinkan)\n\n5. Noise control:\n- Abaikan perubahan kecil (typo, formatting, comment)\n- Hindari false positive\n- Jangan report jika tidak ada issue signifikan\n\n6. Final result:\n- Status: PASS / FAIL\n- Total score\n- Category scores (yang relevan saja)\n- Failed checks (jika ada)\n\n7. History tracking:\n- Append ke: kiro/memory/quality_history.json\n- Jika file tidak ada, buat baru\n- Format:\n{\n  \"feature\": \"nama task/fitur\",\n  \"score\": number,\n  \"status\": \"pass/fail\",\n  \"category_scores\": {},\n  \"failed_checks\": [],\n  \"trend\": \"improving/declining/stable\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"ISO 8601\"\n}\n\n8. Trend calculation:\n- Bandingkan dengan entry terakhir\n- Jika score naik → improving\n- Jika turun → declining\n- Jika sama → stable\n\n9. Optimization:\n- Jangan duplikasi history\n- Pastikan JSON valid\n- Fokus pada insight, bukan jumlah temuan"
  }
}